Considerations and Limitations for Bring Your Own Channel

Before starting your setup process, review the considerations and limitations for Bring Your Own Channel.

This article applies to: Bring Your Own Channel. This article doesn’t apply to: Messaging for In-App, Messaging for Web, standard and enhanced WhatsApp, standard and enhanced Facebook Messenger, standard and enhanced SMS, and enhanced Apple Messages for Business channels

Setup
You can associate one Conversation Channel Definition with multiple messaging channels.

Agent Experience
Bring Your Own Channel supports the following components in text format: Questions with Static Options, Notifications, Time Selectors, and Enhanced Links.
Bring Your Own Channel doesn’t support dynamic content in messaging components.
title: Considerations for Custom Messaging Channels
